  "title": "Service Engineer (Semiconductor) [Woodlands | 5 days | up to $3500] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3>Field Service Engineer (Laser machine & Semiconductor Equipment)</h3><p><strong>5 days, Mon-Fri 8.30am-5.30pm</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $2,800 - $3,500</strong></p><p><strong>Location: Woodlands</strong></p><p><strong>Job scopes:</strong></p><ul><li>Install, troubleshoot, repair & service of laser machine.</li><li>Carry out regular maintenance, repairing of equipment/machines and follow up on work orders, onsite-support equipment/machines installation</li><li>Serves as company contact point with customer on technical matters</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in Electrical /Electronic/ Mechanical Engineering</li><li>1-2 years working experience in Laser Application Equipment and Semiconductor Industrial, knowledge of electrical & mechatronics.</li></ul><p><br />Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
